3. DETECT TRANSCRIPT TYPE
   - Infer from content characteristics
   - Valid types: podcast, meeting, interview, video, webinar, other

4. CALCULATE QUALITY METRICS
   - Completeness Score (0–1): how complete the transcript appears
   - Content Quality Score (0–1): quality and readability of extracted content
   - Speaker Clarity Score (0–1, optional): how clearly speakers are identified
   - Timestamp Accuracy Score (0–1, optional): if timestamps present, how accurate they appear

